{"tid":177551,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"清算第二波　鎖定佔中39人岑敖暉：政府阻嚇大規模街頭運動","createTime":"2017-03-29T02:43:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-02T12:30:30.000Z","uid":30561,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"207e0af381a60736aff4752f8bbd3d9faf7bb0ca","tid":177551,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T02:43:42.000Z","msg":"清算第二波　鎖定佔中39人岑敖暉：政府阻嚇大規模街頭運動<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20170329/19973512\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20170329%2F19973512&d=2Jo0d4zpMW7MEYOmRW2Ldf7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=f6d76018\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20170329%2F19973512&h=bd5f00a9\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20170329/19973512</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】佔中三子等9名參與佔領運動的人士，日前被警方以普通法下的「公眾妨擾罪」等落案起訴。據了解，警方不排除有另一波拘捕行動。消息指警方於佔中後，集中調查48位擔任主導角色的知名人士，繼日前拘捕其中9位後，警方亦已完成其餘39人的調查工作，正徵詢律政司法律意見，一旦有足夠證據，或會提出檢控。學聯前副秘書長岑敖暉對有關消息並不意外，更批評政府藉是次清算行動，阻嚇大規模街頭運動再次發生。<br />\n記者：紀靜雯<br />\n<br />\n消息透露，警方於佔中後，集中調查48位被捕後獲釋的帶頭者，其中9人日前已被落案起訴「公眾妨擾」等罪名。而餘下39人，包括雙學成員黃之鋒、岑敖暉及壹傳媒創辦人黎智英等，據悉警方亦已完成有關的調查工作，正等候律政司法律意見，一旦有足夠證據，或會提出檢控。<br />\n消息續指，其餘數百名被捕的佔中參與者，警方則傾向予以警告，未必提出檢控，惟最終仍需要視乎律政司意見再作決定。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n黃之鋒：被控屬意料之內<br />\n就警方預約拘捕及起訴參與佔領運動人士，曾經是傘運標記的學聯前副秘書長岑敖暉表示，對於自己或會被檢控一事不感意外。他批評，政府是看準時機，待旺角騷亂參與者被判刑及一切選舉完結後，才開始對佔中人士進行拘捕，目的是藉清算行動，阻嚇大規模街頭運動再次發生。<br />\n前學民思潮召集人黃之鋒稱，自己主張公民抗命，認為日後或被檢控屬意料之內，「都唔會有咩擔心，都係平靜嘅心情去面對」。對於警方以「公眾妨擾」罪名起訴佔中人士，他指自己不太理解亦不熟悉有關控罪的內容，「冇記錯呢條條例入罪係可以坐多啲，但我哋都問緊法律團隊意見」。<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20170329/large/29la3p3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170329%2Flarge%2F29la3p3.jpg&h=33477fdc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20170329/large/29la3p2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170329%2Flarge%2F29la3p2.jpg&h=ffed7f42&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20170329/large/29la3p4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170329%2Flarge%2F29la3p4.jpg&h=398276c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陳志全質疑為何拖延至今<br />\n人民力量立法會議員陳志全指，他在參與時已有心理準備終有一日會被檢控，「睇吓遲定早」，但質疑警方為何拖延至今才作檢控，又以「公眾妨擾」罪名落案起訴，認為與過往「告法唔同」，擔心政府是藉刑罰較重的條例打壓佔中人士，「令到人驚，咁可以打壓大型集會出現」。他指如日後一旦被檢控，會看控罪是否合理才決定認罪與否。<br />\n警方回覆表示，作為一個專業的執法部門，其主要職責是維護法紀，不偏不倚地處理所有違法行為，並會根據案情及證據，以專業的態度作出適當的跟進行動。<br />\n律政司發言人回覆指，就所有檢控決定，均是根據相關證據、適用法律和《檢控守則》獨立地作出，不受任何干涉。就案件個別被捕人士的處理方向，律政司不會作評論，但必定會遵守上述方式公平地處理。  <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20170329/large/29la3p5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170329%2Flarge%2F29la3p5.jpg&h=f528765b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n777選舉後一日  佔領行動事隔2年多後再有檢控 : 未來約千人被捕  <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/174928/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/174928/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.epochtimes.com/assets/uploads/2014/09/1409241818472147.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.epochtimes.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2014%2F09%2F1409241818472147.jpg&h=07541d92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170327/photo/bkn-20170327111541695-0327_00822_001_01p.jpg?20170327112945\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170327%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170327111541695-0327_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20170327112945&h=f7b36c5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20140902/large/1409658984_082b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20140902%2Flarge%2F1409658984_082b.jpg&h=34ccf02d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20140928/large/1411839891_bf91.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20140928%2Flarge%2F1411839891_bf91.png&h=cc801a7a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.news.now.com/newsimage/NewsImage/STRIKE.TAMAR.2300.2409.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.news.now.com%2Fnewsimage%2FNewsImage%2FSTRIKE.TAMAR.2300.2409.jpg&h=44e39624&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"85361a69d3bd3642a1a4cec29ffaa2e43be3bdaf","tid":177551,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T02:48:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5b451ca081d57a23f20d3bf4919058f55bf6e19","tid":177551,"uid":522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T02:51:09.000Z","msg":"公民抗命 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88098d16985e2ee41a5e1c69cd0f334f2f29367d","tid":177551,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T02:52:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>公民抗命 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好似簽署了佔中同意書"},{"pid":"6463c6ad35756ad7f714bf0a1ddced2fa88f7f91","tid":177551,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T02:52:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>公民抗命 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好似簽署了佔中同意書</blockquote><br />\n好似話承諾不反抗、配合被捕喎。"},{"pid":"d79525a2c55f6cf1d7cba5731d08b40d6067e825","tid":177551,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T02:55:20.000Z","msg":"蕭若元到中區警署自首<br />\n<img src=\"http://news.memehk.com/img/post/1776_2014-12-23_204949.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.memehk.com%2Fimg%2Fpost%2F1776_2014-12-23_204949.jpg&h=addb1b23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《謎米香港》創辦人蕭若元先生，剛到中區警署自首，隨行律師表示，警方按過去處理佔領人士自首方法，需填上表格並發出登記編號，現時未有拘捕行動。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n蕭若元表示，自己曾到金鐘夏愨道參與集結，在警方安排下填上個人資料及相關內容。<br />\n<br />\n- See more at: <a href=\"http://news.memehk.com/posts/%E8%95%AD%E8%8B%A5%E5%85%83%E5%88%B0%E4%B8%AD%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%A6%E7%BD%B2%E8%87%AA%E9%A6%96#sthash.VmhzXM04.dpuf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.memehk.com%2Fposts%2F%25E8%2595%25AD%25E8%258B%25A5%25E5%2585%2583%25E5%2588%25B0%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E7%25BD%25B2%25E8%2587%25AA%25E9%25A6%2596%23sthash.VmhzXM04.dpuf&d=2Jo0d4zpMW7MEYOmRW2Ldf7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=4ccca5a5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.memehk.com/posts/%E8%95%AD%E8%8B%A5%E5%85%83%E5%88%B0%E4%B8%AD%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%A6%E7%BD%B2%E8%87%AA%E9%A6%96#sthash.VmhzXM04.dpuf</a>"},{"pid":"de2b8d1dba33877c1319cc95a9c91efd68adf9b6","tid":177551,"uid":59773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T03:01:06.000Z","msg":"唔拉鳩你地，你地又點坐到監，以完善法治呀？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5039943b8e0cd52d5051b09a065b43f1223e1b2","tid":177551,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T03:12:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔拉鳩你地，你地又點坐到監，以完善法治呀？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/